--- Hi everyone ! ---

Here is the second version of my map, I changed the name because the older one was already taken. Again, I'll ask you to look for bugs, and tell them to me. The map is still in beta and will be in final version soon. ;)

--- Thank you ! ---

PS: If you test the map alone, use the command "phys_pushscale 100" in console to make props moveable! :)
